PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777723866
OL,3,CMan killed in fight remembered as
OL,4,C"precious, curious and full of love"
OL,6,FDaniel Bassett, 26, of no fixed
OL,7,Faddress, is due to appear at Lewes
OL,8,FCrown Court on Friday 1 May - charged
OL,9,Fwith murder and attempted murder.
OL,11,FPaying tribute, Tio's cousin said: "He
OL,12,Floved deeply, especially his brothers,
OL,13,Fwho will carry this loss in their
OL,14,Fhearts forever, and a big part of them
OL,15,Fwill always be missing."
OL,17,F"I will always remember the Tio that
OL,18,Fwe knew as thoughtful, loving, and
OL,19,Ffull of wonder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
