PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777723866
OL,3,CMan killed in fight remembered as
OL,4,C"precious, curious and full of love"
OL,6,FShe added; "Sleep tight big bro... I
OL,7,Fhope you've found peace. You will
OL,8,Fnever be forgotten."
OL,10,FTio's aunt also shared a tribute,
OL,11,Fsaying; "My heart is full of 'what
OL,12,Fifs' and 'whys' for such a beautiful
OL,13,Fyoung man. I will always remember your
OL,14,Fsmile and your quiet, gentle nature.
OL,15,FYou will forever live in my heart."
OL,17,F"Sleep tight, my precious nephew. I
OL,18,Fknow your mum has you now."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
